title: 80% Votes For Mahama In B/A?....They Should Continuing Tickling Themselves - Obiri Boahen
text: The Deputy General Secretary of the New Patriotic Party ( NPP ), Nana Obiri Boahen has pooh poohed on claims made by the chief of Sunyani that President Mahama will win 80 percent of votes in the region in the 2016 elections. Nana Bosoma Asor
